# Copy to `.env.local` to override per-developer (`.env.local` is gitignored).
# Committed defaults already exist: `.env.development` (dev) and
# `.env.production` (prod build) — you normally don't need to set anything.
#
# Validated at startup by web/src/env.ts (zod). A missing or non-URL value
# aborts boot with a readable error rather than silently falling back to the
# wrong origin.

# Absolute base URL for the API host (no trailing slash, no /v1).
#   dev:  http://localhost:10000
#   prod: https://api.hollowcube.net
VITE_API_BASE_URL=http://localhost:10000
